spx.packets

Class AlertError

  • java.lang.Object
    • spx.packets.Alert
      • spx.packets.AlertError

  • public class AlertError
extends Alert
    AlertError

    The AlertError structure is used to report alerts that occur in response to SPx errors.

    This class is kept in sync with the C++ SPxPacketAlertError structure in "SPxPackets.h".

    See Also:
